channel.title: [Alpha - I think] Ranger hats EVERYWHERE
channel.description:
Hi everyone,
I'm having a problem with objects in game. Seems to me that an object has been replaced by a Ranger Hat. Whether or not this item is in game I am still yet to find out, but I have looked in the Item.cfg and cant find anything in there that might tell me whether or not this is a item or not. Could somebody tell me where to look for this? And how to replace it? I understand it will be in my models, But I haven't a clue where to look and looking through 15000 objects is a bit time consuming!
[img]http://i56.tinypic.com/30a9h1h.png[/img]
Thanks!
